今年晚些时候，斯科特（Scott）将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">2025年的Leads Reading＆Leeds</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CHAPPELL-ROAN">带给我Horizo​​n</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CHAPPELL-ROAN">Chappell Roan</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/HOZIER">Hozier</a> 。他最近还谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-scott-wants-to-collaborate-with-sabrina-carpenter-and-taylor-swift-i-have-some-ill-ideas-3837109">他与Sabrina Carpenter和Taylor Swift合作的希望</a>。</p><p>邮局<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-travis-scott-play-role-in-dwayne-johnson-and-john-cenas-shock-ending-to-wwes-elimination-chamber-3842809">观看Travis Scott在Dwayne Johnson和John Cena的震惊中扮演的角色，结束了WWE的“淘汰室”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
在哪里看英国所有奥斯卡提名电影https://www.nme.com/news/film/where-to-watch-oscar-nominated-films-uk-3842630?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=where-to-watch-oscar-nominated-films-ukAdam Starkey Sun, 02 Mar 2025 21:00:49 +0000 Film NewsNewsExplainerOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3842630 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阿德里安·布罗迪（Adrien Brody）在“野蛮主义者”中。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>包括“物质”和“ Anora”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/where-to-watch-oscar-nominated-films-uk-3842630">在英国观看所有奥斯卡奖提名电影的</a>帖子首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阿德里安·布罗迪（Adrien Brody）在“野蛮主义者”中。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2025年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>的提名可能是迄今为止最折衷的，在音乐改编，科幻大片和身体恐怖噩梦之间。</p><p>由柯南·奥布莱恩（Conan O&#39;Brien）主办的第97届奥斯卡金像奖将于3月2日星期日在洛杉矶好莱坞的杜比剧院举行。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-brutalist-review-adrien-brody-guy-pearce-3830465">“野蛮主义者”评论：一部不容错过的电影巨人</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>艾米莉亚·佩雷斯（EmiliaPérez）</em>以13个名义素的身份领先于今年的比赛，其次是<em>野蛮主义者</em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wicked-movie-ariana-grande-cynthia-erivo-3814095"><em>邪恶的</em></a>，每个人都<em>点了点</em>头，并<em>结束了</em>八个。</p><p>这五部电影都是最好的照片，与<em>Anora</em> ， <em>Dune：第二部分</em>，<em>我还在这里</em>，<em>镍男孩</em>和<em>物质</em>。如果您想赶上所有这些电影，这是英国可用的地方。</p><h2>艾米莉亚·佩雷斯（EmiliaPérez） </h2><figure id="attachment_3812081" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812081" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812081" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Emilia_Perez_Saldana_Netflix.jpg" alt="艾米莉亚·佩雷斯（Emilia Perez）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Emilia_Perez_Saldana_Netflix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Emilia_Perez_Saldana_Netflix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Emilia_Perez_Saldana_Netflix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Emilia_Perez_Saldana_Netflix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Emilia_Perez_Saldana_Netflix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Emilia_Perez_Saldana_Netflix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3812081" class="wp-caption-text"> Zoe Saldana和KarlaSofíaGascón在“ Emilia Perez”中。学分：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>雅克·奥迪亚德（Jacques Audiard）的音乐犯罪电影跟随墨西哥卡特尔（Cartel）领导人，他想在律师的帮助下消失并过渡到一个女人。 KarlaSofíaGascón与ZoeSaldaña，Selena Gomez，Adriana Paz和ÉdgarMiírez一起扮演名义角色。</p><p><strong>在哪里观看</strong>： <em>EmiliaPérez</em>可以在Netflix上流式传输。精选电影院也可以放映。</p><h2>一个完全未知的</h2><figure id="attachment_3828712" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828712" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828712" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee_Chalamet_Bob_Dylan.jpg" alt="Timothee Chalamet" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee_Chalamet_Bob_Dylan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee_Chalamet_Bob_Dylan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee_Chalamet_Bob_Dylan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee_Chalamet_Bob_Dylan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee_Chalamet_Bob_Dylan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee_Chalamet_Bob_Dylan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828712" class="wp-caption-text"> TimothéeChalamet饰演鲍勃·迪伦（Bob Dylan），在“一个完全未知”中。图片来源：探照灯图片</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timothee-chalamet">蒂莫西·查拉梅特（TimothéeChalamet）</a>在这部传记片中扮演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-dylan">鲍勃·迪伦（Bob Dylan）</a>的角色，该传记片描绘了音乐家从民间到电器的过渡。其他演员包括爱德华·诺顿，埃勒·范宁，莫妮卡·巴巴罗和博伊德·霍尔布鲁克。</p><p><strong>在哪里观看：</strong><em>一个完全未知的</em>是电影院。这部电影最近可在美国的流媒体平台上购买和租用，因此在迪士尼+之前，应该在英国的Amazon Prime Video和Apple TV上使用。</p><h2>野蛮主义者</h2><figure id="attachment_3830840" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830840" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830840" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brody-Felicity-Brutalist.jpg" alt="阿德里安·布罗迪（Adrien Brody）和菲利西蒂·琼斯（Felicity Jones）在“野蛮主义者”中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brody-Felicity-Brutalist.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brody-Felicity-Brutalist-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brody-Felicity-Brutalist-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brody-Felicity-Brutalist-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brody-Felicity-Brutalist-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Brody-Felicity-Brutalist-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3830840" class="wp-caption-text">阿德里安·布罗迪（Adrien Brody）和菲利西蒂·琼斯（Felicity Jones）在“野蛮主义者”中。学分：A24</figcaption></figure><p>在这部史诗般的戏剧中，大屠杀幸存者是为了追求美国梦而移民美国的。阿德里安·布罗迪（Adrien Brody）是在奥斯卡颁奖典礼上夺得最佳男主角的领先者，这将是2002年的<em>《钢琴家》</em>之后的第二场胜利。</p><p><strong>在哪里观看：</strong><em>野蛮主义者</em>在电影院里。这部电影还可以在Amazon Prime视频和Apple TV上租用或购买。</p><h2>结论</h2><figure id="attachment_3816014" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3816014" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3816014" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Conclave-image.jpg" alt="拉尔夫·费恩斯（Ralph Fiennes）和斯坦利·图奇（Stanley Tucci）在“会议”中。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Conclave-image.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Conclave-image-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Conclave-image-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Conclave-image-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Conclave-image-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Conclave-image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3816014" class="wp-caption-text">拉尔夫·费恩斯（Ralph Fiennes）和斯坦利·图奇（Stanley Tucci）在“会议”中。图片来源：黑熊</figcaption></figure><p>这部政治惊悚片跟随拉尔夫·费恩斯（Ralph Fiennes）担任枢机主教托马斯·劳伦斯（Thomas Lawrence），他在秘密和丑闻中发现自己是下一届教皇的丑闻。这部电影还主演了斯坦利·图奇（Stanley Tucci），约翰·利特哥（John Lithgow），塞尔吉奥·卡斯特利托（Sergio Castellitto）和伊莎贝拉·罗塞利尼（Isabella Rossellini）。</p><p><strong>在哪里观看</strong>：可以在Amazon Prime Video和Apple TV上购买和租用的<em>candave</em> 。现在也在DVD和蓝光上。</p><h2>沙丘：第二部分</h2><figure id="attachment_3591004" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3591004" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3591004" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1260" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-400x252.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-800x504.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-696x438.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-1392x877.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timothee-Chalamet-and-Zendaya-in-Dune_-Part-II-1068x673.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3591004" class="wp-caption-text">沙丘中的TimothéeChalamet和Zendaya：第二部分。信用：华纳兄弟。</figcaption></figure><p>丹尼斯·维伦纽夫（Denis Villeneuve）对弗兰克·赫伯特（Frank Herbert）的科幻经典赛的改编得出了第二章的结尾，因为保罗·阿特雷德斯（Paul Atreides）试图将阿拉基斯的弗里曼人团结起来，反对众议院哈科嫩。全明星阵容包括蒂莫西·查拉梅特，扎达亚，丽贝卡·弗格森，乔什·布洛林，斯特兰·斯卡斯加德，奥斯丁·巴特勒和佛罗伦萨·普格。</p><p><strong>在哪里观看</strong>：<em>沙丘：第二部分</em>可在DVD和Blu-ray上找到。您也可以现在流式传输，或通过Amazon Prime视频，Apple TV和Sky Store购买和租用它。</p><h2>镍男孩</h2><figure id="attachment_3842017" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3842017" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3842017" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Nickel-Boys.jpg" alt="Ethan Herisse和Brandon Wilson在“镍男孩”中。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Nickel-Boys.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Nickel-Boys-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Nickel-Boys-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Nickel-Boys-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Nickel-Boys-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Nickel-Boys-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3842017" class="wp-caption-text"> Ethan Herisse和Brandon Wilson在“镍男孩”中。图片来源：Curzon电影</figcaption></figure><p>根据科尔森·怀特海德（Colson Whitehead）的小说，这部历史戏剧跟随两个非洲裔美国男孩埃尔伍德（Elwood）和特纳（Turner），他们于1960年代佛罗里达州被送往一所虐待的改革学校。这是导演拉梅尔·罗斯（Ramell Ross）的第一部长片，此后几部著名的纪录片。</p><p><strong>在哪里观看</strong>：<em>镍男孩</em>可以在Amazon Prime视频上流式传输。您也可以在Apple TV上以数字方式购买或租用它。</p><h2> Anora </h2><figure id="attachment_3805765" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805765" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805765" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Mikey-Madison-in-Anora.jpg" alt="Mikey Madison在“ Anora”中。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Mikey-Madison-in-Anora.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Mikey-Madison-in-Anora-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Mikey-Madison-in-Anora-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Mikey-Madison-in-Anora-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Mikey-Madison-in-Anora-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Mikey-Madison-in-Anora-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805765" class="wp-caption-text"> Mikey Madison在“ Anora”中。图片来源：电影娱乐/霓虹灯</figcaption></figure><p>迈基·麦迪逊（Mikey Madison）作为脱衣舞娘的表现出色，他与俄罗斯寡头的儿子有旋风浪漫，只是为了使其失控。这是导演肖恩·贝克（Sean Baker）的第八部电影，之后是<em>橘子</em>和<em>佛罗里达项目</em>之类的电影。</p><p><strong>在哪里观看</strong>： <em>Anora</em>可以在Amazon Prime视频，Apple TV和Sky Store上以数字方式购买和租用。</p><h2>我还在这里</h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="我还在这里|官方拖车（2025）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gDunV808Yf4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>费尔南达·托雷斯（Fernanda Torres）领导了这部有关巴西律师和激进主义者尤尼斯·佩瓦（Eunice Paiva）的政治传记戏剧，后者在军事独裁统治下应对丈夫的强迫失踪。除了最佳图片外，这部电影还在最佳国际故事片类别中提名。</p><p><strong>在哪里观看</strong>：<em>我仍然在这里</em>有电影院可用。</p><h2>物质</h2><figure id="attachment_3805948" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805948" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805948" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-substance-demi-moore.jpg" alt="黛咪·摩尔（Demi Moore）作为“物质”中的伊丽莎白" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-substance-demi-moore.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-substance-demi-moore-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-substance-demi-moore-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-substance-demi-moore-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-substance-demi-moore-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-substance-demi-moore-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805948" class="wp-caption-text">黛咪·摩尔（Demi Moore）饰演“物质”中的伊丽莎白（Elisabeth）。学分：穆比</figcaption></figure><p>黛咪·摩尔（Demi Moore）在这部法国人体恐怖电影中扮演褪色的名人伊丽莎白（Elisabeth）闪闪发光，他转向黑市毒品，创造了玛格丽特·富利（Margaret Falley）扮演的年轻版本。其他演员包括丹尼斯·奎德（Dennis Quaid）和爱德华·汉密尔顿·克拉克（Edward Hamilton-Clark）。</p><p><strong>在哪里观看</strong>：<em>该物质</em>可在Amazon Prime Video上通过Mubi进行流式传输。您也可以通过Apple TV和Sky Store以数字方式购买或租用电影。它从2025年3月31日在DVD和蓝光上发布。</p><h2>邪恶</h2><figure id="attachment_3814097" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814097" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3814097" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Glinda-and-Elphaba-in-Wicked.jpg" alt="Ariana Granda是Glinda，Cynthia Erivo是邪恶的Elphaba" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Glinda-and-Elphaba-in-Wicked.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Glinda-and-Elphaba-in-Wicked-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Glinda-and-Elphaba-in-Wicked-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Glinda-and-Elphaba-in-Wicked-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Glinda-and-Elphaba-in-Wicked-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Glinda-and-Elphaba-in-Wicked-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3814097" class="wp-caption-text"> Ariana Granda是Glinda，Cynthia Erivo是“邪恶”的Elphaba。图片来源：环球影城</figcaption></figure><p>辛西娅·埃里沃（Cynthia Erivo）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">阿丽亚娜·格兰德（Ariana Grande）</a>领导着舞台音乐剧的改编，由<em>疯狂的丰富亚洲人</em>导演乔恩·M·楚（Jon M. Chu）主持。这只是音乐剧的前半部分，第二部电影<em>《 Wicked：Good</em> 》将于2025年11月21日发行。</p><p><strong>在哪里观看</strong>： <em>Wicked</em>可以在Amazon Prime视频，Apple TV和Sky Store上以数字方式购买或租用。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/where-to-watch-oscar-nominated-films-uk-3842630">在英国观看所有奥斯卡奖提名电影的</a>帖子首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
